{"tid":1808400,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不如試下民陣試下平日搞大遊行？","createTime":"2020-01-02T10:41:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-03T02:40:34.000Z","uid":203454,"like":18,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"67fadef60e3c163bef5c5714630ed083a155a794","tid":1808400,"uid":203454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:41:05.000Z","msg":"呢個Idea都係啱啱睇其中一個post有人講起<br />\n發覺我哋次次都係星期日搞大遊行<br />\n不如民陣搵次試下喺平日搞遊行<br />\n變相三罷之餘又可以做個小小嘅統計<br />\n睇下香港其實有幾多人願意罷工罷課？<br />\n但係咁樣嘅話就唔會有平時星期日遊行嘅人數<br />\n所以只係一個測試性質嘅遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28b70f3e026e9a75d587117db9fd3bcc32d24727","tid":1808400,"uid":203454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:41:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c0345d5b51cc9c69debf7519afec0a3edfd40d83","tid":1808400,"uid":203454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:42:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9185b741ea8ec5c160d7dd1119cb4fa7563e07cc","tid":1808400,"uid":203454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:43:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a23c3e5f298dad1ab6f3963c55cf177130c95937","tid":1808400,"uid":275648,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:44:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"879f8c9bc626767329253b7762e1255fe4b94440","tid":1808400,"uid":220787,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:44:53.000Z","msg":"可以一試"},{"pid":"d6f36f0424e5da7e310b31db9c229471569d2efe","tid":1808400,"uid":285899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:45:33.000Z","msg":"可以一試，有既話會join，但唔好抱太大期望會多人"},{"pid":"ed96ee392a0208c8b9d13c63197ea3b023b80375","tid":1808400,"uid":203454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a23c3e5f298dad1ab6f3963c55cf177130c95937","tid":1808400,"uid":275648,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:44:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:45:46.000Z",